Core
~~~~
[+] Command line option to run SIM with specified profile.
[+] Option to show contact list title in message window title.
[+] Contact list: search in contact list by a substring in contact name.
[+] History: option to use external viewer.
[+] Contact list: search in closed contact list groups too.
[-] Contact list: fix deleting contacts by pressing Del.
[*] Remove Qt2 code.
[*] Use QLibrary for plugins instead of libltdl.
[+] Contact list: search in contact list by user protocol IDs.
[+] Add profile (re)naming feature.
[-] Fix context menu shortcuts in dialog window.
[+] Save state on system logout with Qt Session Management.
[-] Win32: fix (un)setting autostart.
[-] Fix restoring font sizes.
[-] Disable history filter when it is empty.
[+] Replace libxml2-based SAX parser with Qt-provided one.
[+] Show user avatars in the dialog window.
[-] Remove "To container" menu when separate containers are disabled.
[*] Auto scroll message view only if it is scrolled to the bottom.
[-] XFree: fix problems with Composite extension enabled.
[-] Refix jisp inclusion
[-] Fix icons packing
[-] Default Accept in DND/Occupied set enabled
[-] Fix loosing configure files on pressing "cancel" button in "Select Profile" window.
[-] Fix loosing configure files on shutdown when "Select Profile" is opened.
[+] Now sim really processes set subscription iq
[-] Do not crash when _host string is NULL in SIMClientSocket::connect (Sim-IM Crashed when trying to receive file in Jabber)
[-] Added GPL-Icons
[-] Several fixes in PluginManager::execute
[-] Fix color-bug in contactlist from send contacts and send multi-message in container
[/] Tested around with vista-homedir.. ==> Comment added
[-] Fix for Bug #11221: Send button for "Authorization request" is always disabled, when request is sending from message window menu. 
[-] Filetransfer: Skip -> Ask - wrong descision for resuming, skip is very bad
[-] Fix: Main toolbar position not restored
[-] OpenDirectory after Filetransfer finished should work now.
[-] Write in profile-independent _core config only the values that are required for profile management. 
[-] Fix create File in Filetransfer.
[-] Fix error messages about uninitialised variables while saving config
[-] Make Alternate-Accelerators unique for Interface (+German)
[-] Use more safe conversion from SIM::clientData* into ICQUserData*, It will at least warn when the wrong conversion occurred...

ICQ plugin
~~~~~~~~~~
[*] Improve client versions detection.
[-] Do not delete contacts if group changed while offline.
[*] Accept messages in Occupied/DND modes by default.
[+] Add new icons from ICQ 5 and ICQ 5.1.
[+] Add MD5 auth support for ICQ accounts.
[-] Fix user info saving.
[-] Fix birthday flag handling.
[-] Sync language and occupation lists with ICQ server.
[*] Disable "Automatically use HTTP polling if proxy required" by
    default.
[+] Send and detect SIM patchlevel in version info.
[-] Fix receiving certain messages containing TLV(5) twice.
[-] Fix playing sounds for messages from QIP.
[-] Login fixed, version changed.
[-] Fix web-aware, www status
[-] On AOL-server error sim tries to reconnect to the server. Two sockets, both connected to the server... Now only one is used.
[-] Fix for some ICQ passwords
[-] Allow sendfile for ICQ6, in spite it is not ready now.
[-] Some Oscar-Filetransfer improvements.
[-] Fix crash: compare of incompatible list operators due to wrong scope/area
[-] ICQ-Filetransfer Reactivation, should work un-NAT'ed between SIM<->SIM. The old ICQ-FT-Method
[-] ICQ-Refactoring: OSCAR-Family => OSCAR-Foodgroup
[-] In-/visible fixed: MSN, Yahoo joined contacts with other protocol does not crash any longer
[-] Fix on multiple Error-Messages in Icqlists
[-] Fix crash when sim-im goes offline while some messages is still sending in ICQ (related to bug #11061, but crash issue is not descibed there)

Jabber plugin
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
[-] Fix crash on auth request when "Receive message only from contacts from list".
[-] Fix handling of single quotes in roster item names.
[+] Add icons for sms and gadu-gadu transports.
[*] Detect jabber transports by missing "@" symbol in jid instead of "/registered" ending.
[+] Allow auth messages for transports.
[*] Show protocol icons for jabber transports in roster.
[*] Ignore JID letter case.
[+] Add support for XEP-0092 client version info requests/replies.
[*] Show resource as a part of JID in contact tip, not as separate line.
[*] Remove SIM version from default resource value.
[+] Support for Jabber's own encryption protocol
[-] Fix: Sim-IM crashes when trying to send contact (Contact List menu option)
[-] Fix: Jabber::Occupied is now available
[-] Hotfix for bug #12510: Problem with connetcing to google-talk on some OSes with openssl 0.9.8g
[-] JabberMessage: Deleted Ambigous "Ctrl+L"
[-] Fix problems with apostrophe in resource name. I.e. shaplov@sim-im.org/It's_me

Yahoo! plugin
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
[-] Login fixed, version changed.

